Package com.iantapply.wynncraft.database.model

Class PlayerModel

java.lang.Object
com.iantapply.wynncraft.database.model.PlayerModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Model
public class PlayerModel extends Object implements Model
A model that is used to handle and store the base profile data of a player who is registered on the server.

All profile related data is stored in the profiles table on a per-profile basis
